      "Title": "NS.UnifiedLoot.ExpandResultsStrategy<T>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/NS.UnifiedLoot.ExpandResultsStrategy-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Replaces individual results with an expanded collection — useful for &quot;drop sets&quot;\nwhere one logical item resolves into a group of concrete items.</p>\n<p>\nFor each result, the <code>expander</code> delegate is called. If it returns a non-null\ncollection, the original result is removed and replaced with one <xref href=\"NS.UnifiedLoot.LootResult%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>\nper expanded item (quantity defaults to 1 unless an optional <code>quantityResolver</code>\nis provided).  If the delegate returns <code>null</code>, the result passes through unchanged.\n</p>\n"
    },
